    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマス前のある日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "月ストの単独ライブ……琴乃の誕生日……\nそしてクリスマスパーティー……",
      "startTime": 7.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "今年のクリスマスは\n楽しいことが目白押しですわ！",
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "随分と嬉しそうだが\nクリスマスがそんなに楽しみなのか？",
      "startTime": 17.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "当然です！　今もクリスマスライブに向けて\n新曲を作っていますが……",
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで話し合い、曲がどんどん形になっていくのが\n楽しいですわ！",
      "startTime": 29.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、琴乃に内緒で集まって\n誕生日のサプライズを計画するのも楽しいですわ！",
      "startTime": 34.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスパーティーに向けて\nツリーや飾り付けを準備するのは楽しいですわ～！",
      "startTime": 40.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "楽しそうで何よりだが、あまり浮かれ過ぎないようにな",
      "startTime": 44.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "浮かれてなんかいませんわ\n私はいつだって冷静沈着ですの",
      "startTime": 50.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そっちこそ、本音では私達のクリスマスパーティーに\n参加したいのではございませんの？",
      "startTime": 58.2,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}